flowchart LR
    SI[Scope Intake]
    DI[Discovery]
    FI[Filtering]
    MI[Mining]
    SC[Scoring & Prioritization]
    EX[Execution / Scanners]
    AN[Analysis & Detection]
    RP[Reporting & Reports]
    DB[Dashboard (FastAPI + SSE)]
    WQ[Workers / Queue]
    INF[Infrastructure (Cache, Storage, Observability)]

    SI --> DI
    DI --> FI
